gwt.material.design.client.base.viewport

Interface ViewPortFallback


  • public interface ViewPortFallback
    View Port Fallback.

    Return true to continue propagating view port detection, false to break.

    Note that if ViewPortHandler.propagateFallback(boolean) is not true, this will only be called if no Resolution matches are made. Otherwise the fallback is called upon every failed Resolution match and can be propagated (or not propagated) with its call result.
    Author:
    Ben
